About this item

  • Premium Quality Foil Mini Pie Pans: Made of premium quality, heavy-duty aluminum foil, our disposable pie tins are designed to be multifunctional - you can store, bake, and serve all in one dish! Great for takeout, catering, food tastings, bake sales, parties, and more!
  • High Gauge Aluminum: Our aluminum foil pie pans have 45 gauge and full curl rim for sturdiness and durability. You can cook your heaviest tarts and thick meat pies without worrying about the pans breaking or ripping.
  • Easy Storage: Our small pie pans are designed to fit into one another to help reduce storage space. Cleanup is even easier - simply toss when youre done! Our pie pans are disposable and recyclable!
  • Versatile: Use our mini disposable pie tins to cook single serve sweet treats like pies, fruit & egg tarts, mini cheese cakes, and apple crisps. Or cook savory appetizers like baked mac n cheese, meat/veggie pies, quiches, and cheese tarts. Perfect for restaurants, cafes, bistros, or bakeries, and more!
  • Great Value Pack: Our value pack comes with 50 6-inch disposable aluminum baking small pie pans round with a 6 ounce capacity. Top Diameter: 5 7/8 Inner Diameter: 5 3/4 Bottom Diameter: 4 Depth: 3/4

Stock Your Home Mini Pie Pans

Premium Quality Aluminum Foil

Our Pie Pans are designed to be multifunctional - you can store, bake, and serve all in one dish! Made of premium quality, heavy-duty aluminum foil, our pie pans are oven-safe, freezer safe, recyclable, and disposable.

With a high gauge and full curl rim for durability, you can cook your heaviest tarts and thick meat pies without worrying about the pans breaking or ripping. They are too stackable, helping you save storage space.

  • Please read our pie pan measurements to ensure you get the right sized pan to suit your baking needs

Single Portion

Impress your guests by making beautiful individual desserts or savory dishes with these tins!

Stackable

Designed to take up minimal storage space, these pans sit nicely inside one another.

Oven Safe

These pans can go from your counter to your freezer, and straight into the oven!

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
